node.text: Casting told me I was playing hard to get. I received these phone calls from @tiffanycasting and kept wondering what she wanted. I listened to her voicemail and gave her a phone call back. That phone call changed my life ❤️ After days in Cali and weeks in the UK; anxiety, tears, stress, anger, sickness, happiness, laughter, memories, experiences...I have made friendships that will last a lifetime. Wouldn’t change it for the world.

node.text: Finally I can tell everyone!!! I'm so excited to finally be able to announce that I am going to be on @TheCircleNetflix,  a new reality-competition series where players can be whoever it takes to win.  #TheCircle, a Netflix three-week event, starts Jan 1.
